    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>People who use cameras, particularly those who operate motion picture, video, or television cameras professionally. The term is used whether the person is male or female. For persons who oversee all the aspects of photography in a filmmaking, video, or television project, see "cinematographers."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000021311/ILO, International Standard Classification of Occupations (1969)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Operadores de cámaras de cine, video o televisión. Para personas que supervisan todos los aspectos de fotografía en una producción cinematográfica, de video o proyecto de televisión, use "cinematógrafo".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mensen die film- of televisiecameras bedienen. Gebruik 'cineasten' voor de personen die toezicht houden op alle fotografische aspecten tijdens het maken van een film of televisieproject.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>操作電影或電視拍攝用攝影機的從業人員。若為負責監控電影製片或電視節目攝影品質的從業人員，則稱之為「攝影技師」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
